		    	<li>Use the Hint if Needed</li>
		    </ul>
		    <br>
		    <p class="text-center">Click the Right Arrow when you are ready!</p>
		  </div>
		  <div class="modal-footer">
		  	<p id="beginnerModalFooter">Challenge Your Friends! <br> And Google what you don't know!</p>
